Odaily Planet Daily News Cobo co-founder and CEO Yu X said in a post that Bybit's $1.5 billion security incident and multiple Safe owner tampering incidents exposed the three major pain points of blockchain security: 
1. The front-end/plug-in is easily tampered with, and users cannot verify signature data; 
2. The multi-signature key holder environment lacks independence and has no mandatory audit mechanism; 
3. The hardware wallet has weak transaction parsing capabilities and is basically in a blind signing state;
